read(BufferedReader) - Static method in class ch.supertomcat.bh.importexport.ImportLinkList
Reads the textfile and detects if it's a file generated from a Browser-Plugin or a normal one link per line textfile The textfile generated from Browser-Plugins must have in the first 3 lines have this information: BH{af2f0750-c598-4826-8e5f-bb98aab519a5} Title Referrer Then it can be a link per line or a link then a tab and then a thumbnail-URL per line Example: http://img207.imagevenue.com/img.php?
